</span></p><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-4231_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-4233_">The theme for Purple Light Up Day 2023, "Shining a Light on Accessibility and Innovation," is a compelling call to action, emphasising that true inclusivity goes beyond simply recognising diversity. It's about proactively creating a workspace where individuals of all abilities can not only participate but also excel and innovate.
<br><br>This theme underscores the importance of designing environments that are accessible and conducive to the unique contributions of every individual, fostering a culture of innovation that benefits from the full spectrum of human talent and perspectives.
<br>

</span></p><h2 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-4234_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-4236_">Key definitions
