</li><li tabindex="0" spellcheck="false" data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-bQtKYq wvgEH pf-4241_"><b>Disability inclusion</b> - The practice of ensuring that people with disabilities have equal access to opportunities, resources, and benefits, creating an environment that values their unique abilities and perspectives.
</li></ul><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu NrNIR pf-4243_ _Y6RW61"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-4245_">Illuminating the workplace with inclusivity
