</span></h3><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-4253_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-4255_">Organisations actively participate in Purple Light Up Day by organising events such as awareness sessions, workshops, and panel discussions highlighting the contributions of disabled individuals in various fields.
