</span></h3><p class="sc-FNXRL jGHEAN pf-4259_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gyElHZ fxaypC pf-4261_">Purple Light Up Day encourages companies to showcase their commitment to accessibility and innovation by unveiling new initiatives, technologies, or policies that enhance the working experience for individuals with disabilities.
